item.title: How do you get your server online?
item.dc:creator: @Josh21210 Josh21210
item.description:
@Josh21210 wrote:

When you open no ip…

Did you click on the check next to your server ip?

If not do that…

Next Is the little Emoticon have a face with sunglasses or is it blushing?

If sunglasses then un check the box and recheck it.

If that does not work then its probably something with port forwarding.

and If its not wrong with the port Forwarding then Its Probably Something Wrong with Enviromental Variables.

Hope i helped you.

Josh
